I saw many comments in the chat saying things along the lines of her being tired after 10 to 15 minutes of exercise. People need to be more forgiving to Rushia as it was apparent she was having difficulty with breathing. 

Please don't overdo it in the future Rushia. Your health is the most important thing and I'm sure you don't want to cause much worry to your fans. We all love you Rushia so please try to not do anything that could jeopardize your health. :_ãƒãƒ¼ãƒˆ::_ãƒãƒ¼ãƒˆ::_ãƒãƒ¼ãƒˆ:
